      <title>【可视化】搜索组件（1）</title>
      <link href="/2021/12/20/%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E5%8F%AF%E8%A7%86%E5%8C%96%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89/"/>
      <url>/2021/12/20/%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E5%8F%AF%E8%A7%86%E5%8C%96%EF%BC%881%EF%BC%89/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>由于每次遇到搜索栏都要写一遍，于是有了搞一个可视化配置来处理搜索的布局以及配置的想法。</p><h2 id="项目地址"><a href="#项目地址" class="headerlink" title="项目地址"></a>项目地址</h2><p><a href="https://github.com/hystericalPerson/visualization">项目地址</a><br><a href="https://github.com/hystericalPerson/visualization">https://github.com/hystericalPerson/visualization</a></p><h2 id="需要的功能"><a href="#需要的功能" class="headerlink" title="需要的功能"></a>需要的功能</h2><ol><li>必要的搜索配件（input，date等）</li><li>布局配置以及元素配置（每个元素可能会不一致）</li><li>渲染配置的区域实现</li><li>按钮：预览，导出布局和导出搜索配置</li></ol><h2 id="布局配置"><a href="#布局配置" class="headerlink" title="布局配置"></a>布局配置</h2><p>布局配置为公共配置:</p><ol><li>行数</li><li>垂直间距</li><li>水平间距</li><li>搜索组件的默认大小</li><li>是否展示label</li><li>是否需要拓展搜索</li></ol><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;template&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;div class=&quot;config-module&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;div class=&quot;config-info&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;p class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;行数&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">              &lt;a-select</span><br><span class="line">                v-model:value=&quot;configInfo.layoutConfig.columnCount&quot;</span><br><span class="line">                style=&quot;width:100%&quot;</span><br><span class="line">            &gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;a-select-option :value=&quot;1&quot;&gt;1&lt;/a-select-option&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;a-select-option :value=&quot;2&quot;&gt;2&lt;/a-select-option&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;a-select-option :value=&quot;3&quot;&gt;3&lt;/a-select-option&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;a-select-option :value=&quot;4&quot;&gt;4&lt;/a-select-option&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;/a-select&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;div class=&quot;config-info&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;p class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;垂直间距&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;a-input-number v-model:value=&quot;configInfo.layoutConfig.verticalGutter&quot; :precision=&quot;0&quot; :min=&quot;8&quot; :max=&quot;48&quot; class=&quot;width100&quot;/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;div class=&quot;config-info&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;p class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;水平间距&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;a-input-number v-model:value=&quot;configInfo.layoutConfig.horizontalGutter&quot; :precision=&quot;0&quot; :min=&quot;8&quot; :max=&quot;48&quot;  class=&quot;width100&quot;/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;div class=&quot;config-info&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;p class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;默认大小&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;a-select</span><br><span class="line">                v-model:value=&quot;configInfo.layoutConfig.size&quot;</span><br><span class="line">                style=&quot;width:100%&quot;</span><br><span class="line">            &gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;a-select-option value=&quot;small&quot;&gt;小&lt;/a-select-option&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;a-select-option value=&quot;default&quot;&gt;正常&lt;/a-select-option&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;a-select-option value=&quot;large&quot;&gt;大&lt;/a-select-option&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;/a-select&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;div class=&quot;config-info&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;p class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;默认文案是否在label展示&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;a-radio-group v-model:value=&quot;configInfo.layoutConfig.isLabel&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;a-radio :value=&quot;true&quot;&gt;是&lt;/a-radio&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;a-radio :value=&quot;false&quot;&gt;否&lt;/a-radio&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;/a-radio-group&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;div class=&quot;config-info&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;p class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;是否需要拓展搜索&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;a-radio-group v-model:value=&quot;configInfo.layoutConfig.isExtend&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;a-radio :value=&quot;true&quot;&gt;是&lt;/a-radio&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;a-radio :value=&quot;false&quot;&gt;否&lt;/a-radio&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;/a-radio-group&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/template&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="渲染区域"><a href="#渲染区域" class="headerlink" title="渲染区域"></a>渲染区域</h2><p>根据组件数量和布局配置和元素配置共同实现</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;template&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;div class=&quot;render-box&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">         &lt;a-form&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;!-- &#123;&#123;configInfo.renderList&#125;&#125; --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;a-row :gutter=&quot;[configInfo.layoutConfig.horizontalGutter, configInfo.layoutConfig.verticalGutter]&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;a-col v-for=&quot;item in configInfo.renderList&quot; :key=&quot;item.type&quot; :span=&quot;(item.isCustomWidth &amp;&amp; item.customWidth) || (24/configInfo.layoutConfig.columnCount)&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                    &lt;div @click=&quot;onClickFormItem(item)&quot; :class=&quot;&#123;isActive: item.key === isActiveKey &#125;&quot; style=&quot;height:100%;&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        &lt;div v-if=&quot;item.isSlot&quot; class=&quot;slot&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                            插槽</span><br><span class="line">                        &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                        &lt;component :is=&quot;item.type + &#x27;Components&#x27;&quot; :config=&quot;item&quot; v-else&gt;&lt;/component&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                    &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;/a-col&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;/a-row&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/a-form&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/template&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>component</code>根据不同组件实现不同的功能</p><h2 id="元素都有的配置"><a href="#元素都有的配置" class="headerlink" title="元素都有的配置"></a>元素都有的配置</h2><ol><li>默认标题</li><li>标题的字段</li><li>是否为拓展</li><li>是否有自定义宽度以及数值</li><li>是否需要插槽</li></ol><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;template&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;div v-if=&quot;configInfo.domConfig&quot; class=&quot;config-module&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;!-- 组件公共配置 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;div class=&quot;config-info&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;p class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;默认标题&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;a-input v-model:value=&quot;configInfo.domConfig.name&quot; class=&quot;width100&quot;/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;div class=&quot;config-info&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;p class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;标题字段名称&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;a-input v-model:value=&quot;configInfo.domConfig.key&quot; class=&quot;width100&quot;/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;div class=&quot;config-info&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;p class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;是否为扩展搜索&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;a-radio-group v-model:value=&quot;configInfo.domConfig.isExtend&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;a-radio :value=&quot;true&quot;&gt;是&lt;/a-radio&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;a-radio :value=&quot;false&quot;&gt;否&lt;/a-radio&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;/a-radio-group&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;div class=&quot;config-info&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;p class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;是否设置自定义宽度&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;a-radio-group v-model:value=&quot;configInfo.domConfig.isCustomWidth&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;a-radio :value=&quot;true&quot;&gt;是&lt;/a-radio&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;a-radio :value=&quot;false&quot;&gt;否&lt;/a-radio&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;/a-radio-group&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;div class=&quot;config-info&quot; v-if=&quot;configInfo.domConfig.isCustomWidth&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;p class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;自定义宽度&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;a-input-number v-model:value=&quot;configInfo.domConfig.customWidth&quot; class=&quot;width100&quot; :min=&quot;1&quot; :max=&quot;24&quot;/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;p class=&quot;tip&quot;&gt;建议设置6，12，18，24&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;div class=&quot;config-info&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;p class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;是否需要插槽&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;a-radio-group v-model:value=&quot;configInfo.domConfig.isSlot&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;a-radio :value=&quot;true&quot;&gt;是&lt;/a-radio&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;a-radio :value=&quot;false&quot;&gt;否&lt;/a-radio&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;/a-radio-group&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;p class=&quot;tip&quot;&gt;插槽名称为字段名称&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;component :is=&quot;getDomType()&quot;&gt;&lt;/component&gt;</span><br><span class="line">         &lt;p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;&#123;configInfo.domConfig&#125;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;div v-else class=&quot;config-module&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        请先选择节点后进行配置</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/template&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
